query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-volley',
'angular6',
'arm',
'asp.net-mvc-2',
'copy',
'dart',
'interface-builder',
'internet-explorer-11',
'jqgrid',
'namespaces',
'oracle11g',
'selenium',
'silverlight');
